abstract: Remains unclear whether Tiger Woods will return to play at 2015 Masters tournament, despite playing practice round at Augusta National.
lead_paragraph: Woods, who has not competed since Feb. 5, played a practice round at Augusta National, but it was unclear whether he would return next week for the Masters.

headline.main: Tiger Woods Plays at Augusta National
